      "@value" : "initial internal resistance"
    },
    "samm:description" : {
      "@language" : "en",
      "@value" : "The battery passport can include additional information about the initial internal resistance on battery module level, if available. It should be defined and calculated analogously as the requirements on battery pack level above.\n\nDIN DKE Spec 99100 chapter reference: 6.7.5.2"
